			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Today we will talk with an IT professional who created a tool to help techs calculate the pricing of work orders on web-based service platforms and find out how you can get it free.</p>
<p><strong>TechPodcasts Promo Tag :10<br />
Intro 1:17<br />
Billboard 1:11</strong></p>
<p><strong>News and Comment segment 4:12</strong><br />
<a target="_blank" title="http://www.acrbo.com/" href="http://www.acrbo.com/">ACRBO</a> announced the launch of a <a target="_blank" title="http://issuu.com/acrbo/docs/acrbojanmag?mode=window&#038;backgroundColor=%23222222" href="http://issuu.com/acrbo/docs/acrbojanmag?mode=window&#038;backgroundColor=%23222222">new magazine</a> for computer business owners.</p>
