<p>Sponsor: MozyPro Online Backup: Simple, Automatic &#038; Secure Backup <a target="_blank" title="http://bit.ly/mozypod1" href="http://bit.ly/mozypod1">http://mozy.com/pro</a>.</p>
<p><a target="_blank" title="http://www.apple.com/pr/library/2012/01/24Apple-Reports-First-Quarter-Results.html" href="http://www.apple.com/pr/library/2012/01/24Apple-Reports-First-Quarter-Results.html">Apple</a> posted a record revenue for its fiscal first quarter of 2012.</p>
<p><a target="_blank" title="http://www.symantec.com" href="http://www.symantec.com">Symantec</a> is telling users to remove its software from their computers.</p>
