<a title="TheForceField.Net" target="_blank" href="http://www.theforcefield.net">The Force Field Web Portal</a> TheForceField.Net</p>
<p><strong>Intro to Topic 1:52</strong><br />
Today we&#8217;re going to talk with Donald Bertrand of <a target="_blank" title="Donald Bertrand Technical Consulting" href="http://www.dbetc.com/">Donald Bertrand Technical Consulting</a>. We will find out how he stays profitable accepting work from web-based service platforms, learn about his <a target="_blank" title="Platform Pricing Tool" href="http://www.theforcefield.net/forums/index.php?topic=5826.msg58089#msg58089">Platform Pricing Tool</a> and find out how we can use it to manage the pricing of platform work in our own business – free.</p>
